Type 'encode' to encrypt, type 'decode' to decrypt:
encode
Type your message:
hello how are you 33
Type the shift number:
33
The encoded message is olssv ovd hyl fvb 33
 Type 'yes' if you want to go again .Otherwise type 'no'yes
Type 'encode' to encrypt, type 'decode' to decrypt:
decode
Type your message:
olssv ovd hyl fvb 33
Type the shift number:
33
The decoded message is hello how are you 33
 Type 'yes' if you want to go again .Otherwise type 'no'no
